data.enText: an Italian dish consisting of a flat round bread base with cheese, tomatoes, vegetables, meat, etc. on top

tr: Italian open pie made of thin bread dough spread with a spiced mixture of e.g. tomato sauce and cheese

value.def: A pizza is a flat, round piece of dough covered with tomatoes, cheese, and other savoury food, and then baked in an oven.

example.ex: We went for a pizza together at lunch-time.
example.tran: 我们中午一起去吃了比萨饼。

trans: 披萨王；批萨国王；美味比萨达人；即食乐餐厅
